import '../css/Classroom.css' function MyclassroomItem(props) { const userInfo = props.userInfo === undefined? {} : props.userInfo const selfClassroomInfo = props.selfClassroomInfo console.log(selfClassroomInfo) return (
name: {userInfo.nickname}
profession: {userInfo.profession === undefined? "loading..." : userInfo.profession[0]}
status: {selfClassroomInfo.status}
description: {self}
time: / points: start
) } export default MyclassroomItem
